Package: microserver
Type: Package
Title: Microserver
Version: 0.0.3
Description: Microserver is a package that builds on the httupv library
    and aims to provide a minimal set of tools to get a JSON-based
    REST API off the ground.
Author: Robert Krzyzanowski <technoguyrob@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Robert Krzyzanowski <technoguyrob@gmail.com>
